title: DIP-019: iW3Fi | Indie Web3 Fashion Index
body:
For this week, we are also starting to open up the forum where now any Global Designer Network designer, and also broader web3 fashion community member, can begin proposing content, realms, NFTs, tokens, DAOs across web3 fashion to be voted into the index. Below are some of the initial proposals to go to vote this week:

*DXM #100549 (https://opensea.io/assets/matic/0x567c7b3364ba2903a80ecbad6c54ba8c0e1a069e/100549)
*African Space Man Suit (https://fashion.digitalax.xyz/product/682/1/0/)
*Observed and Protected by Violetta (https://knownorigin.io/gallery/4910000-observed-and-protected)
*DXM #100548 (https://opensea.io/assets/matic/0x567c7b3364ba2903a80ecbad6c54ba8c0e1a069e/100548 1)
*Rogue One (https://fashion.digitalax.xyz/product/318/1/0/)
*Carbon Collection by Igor (https://twitter.com/starostyuk_igor/status/1468969145253335040)

Voting type: Ranked Choice Voting

Live on Snapshot: Dec 13th 2021

Eligible Voters: $MONA and Genesis MONA NFT holders

Quorum: No
